{"tid":427702,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Cuphead真心難玩] 外國有人連tutorial都過唔到！","createTime":"2017-10-07T15:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T01:27:52.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eb6c19d5ed464576c8347b2e8ad6ea7b36806dbc","tid":427702,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:16:51.000Z","msg":"近日Reddit, Twitter流傳一段Cuphead gameplay，<br />\n片中人連教學關卡都過唔到，<br />\n備受恥笑。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/07/231542_fe9ce677a1137f5e4608347af7c4d184.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F07%2F231542_fe9ce677a1137f5e4608347af7c4d184.png&h=bf1a4235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sYsm5fp-LlQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsYsm5fp-LlQ&d=Bt8vY%2FcGdb2BO3jI8rmSWEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=e2f57f95\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sYsm5fp-LlQ</a></div><br />\n<br />\n唔識打機唔係問題，問題係個玩家叫做Dean Takahashi，職業係遊戲新聞撰稿，佢從事呢行已經有25年，仲出過幾本書，內容係探討遊戲界現象。<br />\n<br />\n發展至此，已經唔係識唔識打機嘅問題，而係Dean嘅專業資格被世人質疑。<br />\n<br />\n有人問Dean玩到咁柒，佢點解好意思上載影片。<br />\n<br />\n面對抨擊，Dean嘅回應同陶傑差唔多: 佢話自己係特登放段片出嚟搏屌，因為佢認為網絡世界好刻薄，所以佢放出嚟就會有更多人轉載，成件事都係佢嘅計算......<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Loui5Ng/posts/2159819397377466\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLoui5Ng%2Fposts%2F2159819397377466&d=Bt8vY%2FcGdb2BO3jI8rmSWEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a8d9371f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Loui5Ng/posts/2159819397377466</a></div>"},{"pid":"97fb9e1a6543cd968755395f8d38768ca43c5c94","tid":427702,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}